# Team 6 - Sprint 2 Review Report

## Sprint Goal

The goal of Sprint 2 was to establish a strong technical foundation for the application. This includes creating the database schema, integrating unit testing, Maven dependency management, code coverage reporting, and creating the UI design.

## Completed User Stories / Tasks

The full Product Backlog and Sprint setup are available in the Trello workspace:
